1%2F01%2Fmewe-chinese03-1.jpg&h=864e3520&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 那麼新介面就全面繁體中文化了！<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/mewe-chinese04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F01%2Fmewe-chinese04.jpg&h=c7693c40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（注意：本站也建立了 MeWe Page &ndash; Apple User Club，請支持）"},{"pid":"cc40e8ed21006585cf3cd8b81240032e12f99ac4","tid":2357835,"uid":60434,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T05:19:03.000Z","msg":"勁撚少人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d55a585c223346a20f40c806f1bf80fb6e677253","tid":2357835,"uid":8171,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"cc40e8ed21006585cf3cd8b81240032e12f99ac4","tid":2357835,"uid":60434,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T05:19:03.000Z","msg":"勁撚少人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T05:23:04.000Z","msg":"有好多人見到無中文介面卻步，所以要廣傳等多啲人用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3afb1c2276c81e2c71f8fb1abeb3315e753bd4f1","tid":2357835,"uid":14543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T05:23:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c05dd82a8d370146fa6d9bf5823a2c2239c119cb","tid":2357835,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T05:24:46.000Z","msg":"心裡凝住會搵個weekend認真玩<br />\n但始終都冇玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91a688048b04f3aa515d17474da8cdd1baa08178","tid":2357835,"uid":149877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T05:29:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c2b1d5c2e23bf724d04f5633cde5b61a598eac6